The Programs submenu has buttons \
that represent programs you can run on the workspace.  \
To display the Programs submenu, drag MENU into the right half \
of the Programs menu button.  \
To choose a button from the Programs submenu, \
drag MENU onto a button and release MENU.

You can edit the Programs submenu from its property \
window to add new programs or remove old ones from the submenu.  \
You access this property window using the Properties \
menu button on the Workspace menu and choosing "Programs Submenu..." \
from the Properties submenu.
